While looking for a link, I came across a site called openpolice.org (https://openpolice.org/dept/MA-boston-police-dept) that said that the BPD has an online form for reporting police misconduct but I was unable to locate it. Then I found in the BPD FAQ (https://bpdnews.com/faq) a section addressing police misconduct reports that said that a "Internal Affairs Complaint Information Form" would need to be filled out and mailed or handed in. The only place I could find that form was on this website http://vault.blackstonian.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/BPD_complaint_form.pdf
